00:43:25,565 --> 00:43:33,530
My partners on the far side even have any level of qualified training to actually do the job of a true dispatch supervisor.

563
00:43:33,951 --> 00:43:39,814
Right now, the dispatches, they're under the watchful eye of a shift commander on the police side.

564
00:43:39,934 --> 00:43:43,417
It's always been that way since the center opened in 1997.

565
00:43:44,397 --> 00:43:51,622
That does not mean that person who is watching them has any level of knowledge regarding the actual 911 process.

566
00:43:51,722 --> 00:43:53,423
We're not qualified to use it at all.

567
00:43:54,430 --> 00:43:56,491
